  • Method Details

    • processRequests

      void processRequests​(long millis) throws IOException, SpinnmanException, InterruptedException
      The core of the scheduler.
      Parameters:
      millis - How many milliseconds to sleep before doing a rerun of the scheduler. If zero (or less), only one run will be done.
      Throws:
      IOException - If talking to the network fails
      SpinnmanException - If a BMP sends an error back
      InterruptedException - If the wait for workers to spawn fails.
